'''跳足鱷'''（學名：''Hallopus''）使種史前[[爬行動物|爬行動物]]，是由[[奧塞內爾·查利斯·馬什|奧塞內爾·查利斯·馬什]]（Othniel Charles Marsh）在1881年命名，當時被歸類於[[恐龍|恐龍]]。跳足鱷可能是種史前鱷類，或可能是種更原始的[[伪鳄类|伪鳄类]]，或是[[準噶爾鱷|準噶爾鱷]]的近親<ref>A. D. Walker. [http://www.jstor.org/discover/10.2307/2417013?uid=3737808&uid=2134&uid=2&uid=70&uid=4&sid=47699016768237 A Revision of the Jurassic Reptile Hallopus victor (Marsh), with Remarks on the Classification of Crocodiles. Philosophical Transactions of the Royal Society of London]. Series B, Biological Sciences Vol. 257, No. 816 (Feb. 26, 1970), pp. 323-372</ref>。跳足鱷是種小型動物，身長估計約1公尺<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://qilong.wordpress.com/2011/05/27/better-know-a-crocbeak-macelognathus-and-hallopus/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919054632/https://qilong.wordpress.com/2011/05/27/better-know-a-crocbeak-macelognathus-and-hallopus/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

